FBIS3-27508 "drchi037_w_94009" FBIS-CHI-94-037 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Feb 1994 HONG KONG & MACAO Hong Kong Zhou Nan Denies Rumor of Transfer to Beijing HK2402063394 Hong Kong TA KUNG PAO in Chinese 18 Feb 94 p 2 HK2402063394 Hong Kong TA KUNG PAO Language: Chinese Article Type:BFN [Report: "Zhou Nan Denies Rumor That He Will Be Transferred to Beijing"] [Text] Zhou Nan, director of the XINHUA Hong Kong Branch, yesterday clarified the rumor that he was to be transferred to Beijing. According to Zhou Nan, a rumor of this kind appears about once a year and may reappear in the future. He said the principle for coping with it was very simple -- "just ignore it." In addition, Deputy Director Zhang Junsheng said that the news was untrue and inaccurate.
